statements: SELECT * FROM swim_meet_registration;
SELECT registration_id, participant_name, event_name FROM swim_meet_registration WHERE participant_age > 18;
SELECT participant_name, participant_gender, event_name FROM swim_meet_registration WHERE event_date = '2022-09-15';
SELECT event_name, participant_age FROM swim_meet_registration WHERE participant_gender = 'M' ORDER BY participant_age DESC;
SELECT MAX(participant_age) AS max_age, MIN(participant_age) AS min_age FROM swim_meet_registration;
SELECT * FROM swim_meet_registration WHERE participant_age > 20 ORDER BY registration_date DESC LIMIT 5;
SELECT participant_name, participant_age, event_name, event_date FROM swim_meet_registration WHERE event_date >= '2022-01-01' ORDER BY event_date ASC;
SELECT event_name, COUNT(*) as total_registrations FROM swim_meet_registration GROUP BY event_name HAVING total_registrations > 3 ORDER BY total_registrations DESC;

SELECT participant_name, participant_age, event_name, registration_date FROM swim_meet_registration WHERE registration_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01 00:00:00' AND '2022-02-01 23:59:59' ORDER BY participant_name ASC;

SELECT participant_name, participant_age, participant_gender, event_name, event_date FROM swim_meet_registration WHERE event_name LIKE '%freestyle%' OR event_name LIKE '%backstroke%' ORDER BY event_date DESC, participant_age DESC;
SELECT * FROM participants;
SELECT participant_name, age FROM participants WHERE age > 25;
SELECT participant_id, participant_name, age FROM participants ORDER BY age DESC;
SELECT * FROM events WHERE location = 'New York';
SELECT event_name, event_date FROM events ORDER BY event_date DESC;
SELECT participant_name, age, team_name FROM participants;
SELECT * FROM participants WHERE age > 25;
SELECT event_name, location FROM events WHERE event_date = '2022-10-20';
SELECT participant_name, team_name FROM participants ORDER BY team_name DESC;
SELECT MAX(age) AS oldest_age, MIN(age) AS youngest_age FROM participants;
SELECT * FROM meet_entries;
SELECT participant_name, participant_age FROM meet_entries;
SELECT meet_name, meet_location FROM meets;
SELECT participant_name, participant_age, participant_email FROM participants;
SELECT meet_name, meet_location, meet_date FROM meets;
SELECT * FROM meets WHERE meet_name = 'Example Meet';
SELECT meet_name, meet_location FROM meets ORDER BY meet_date DESC;
SELECT COUNT(meet_id) AS total_meets FROM meets;
SELECT participant_name, participant_age FROM meet_entries WHERE meet_id = 1;
SELECT * FROM meets WHERE meet_date >= '2022-01-01' AND meet_location = 'City A';
SELECT * FROM meet;
SELECT meet_name, meet_date FROM meet WHERE meet_date >= '2022-01-01';
SELECT * FROM event ORDER BY event_distance DESC;
SELECT participant_name, participant_age FROM participant WHERE participant_gender = 'Female';
SELECT registration_id, meet_id, participant_id FROM registration WHERE registration_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31';
SELECT * FROM meet ORDER BY meet_date DESC, meet_name ASC;
SELECT event_name, event_distance, meet_name FROM event JOIN meet ON event.meet_id = meet.meet_id WHERE event_distance > 10 ORDER BY event_distance DESC;
SELECT participant_name, participant_age, participant_gender FROM participant WHERE participant_age BETWEEN 20 AND 30 AND participant_gender = 'Male';
SELECT meet_name, COUNT(registration_id) AS total_registrations FROM meet LEFT JOIN registration ON meet.meet_id = registration.meet_id GROUP BY meet_name ORDER BY total_registrations DESC;

SELECT meet_name, event_name, participant_name FROM meet JOIN registration ON meet.meet_id = registration.meet_id JOIN event ON registration.meet_id = event.meet_id JOIN participant ON registration.participant_id = participant.participant_id;
SELECT * FROM meet_participants WHERE participant_age > 18;
SELECT participant_name, participant_gender FROM meet_participants WHERE participant_gender = 'Male';
SELECT event_name, event_date FROM events WHERE event_date >= '2023-01-01';
SELECT result_time FROM results ORDER BY result_time DESC;
SELECT team_name, team_location FROM teams WHERE team_location = 'New York';
SELECT * FROM meet_participants WHERE participant_age > 30 ORDER BY participant_name DESC;
SELECT event_name, event_location FROM events WHERE event_date >= '2022-01-01' ORDER BY event_location;
SELECT participant_name, event_name, result_time FROM meet_participants JOIN results ON meet_participants.id = results.participant_id ORDER BY result_time DESC;
SELECT t.team_name, t.team_location, r.result_time FROM teams t JOIN results r ON t.team_id = r.participant_id ORDER BY result_time ASC;

SELECT p.participant_name, e.event_name, r.result_time FROM meet_participants p JOIN registrations reg ON p.id = reg.participant_id JOIN events e ON reg.event_id = e.event_id JOIN results r ON p.id = r.participant_id ORDER BY r.result_time ASC;
